  "WeaponCanUseDes": {
    "Array": [
      "A heavily modified AK, forged in shadow to pierce the void. Each shot echoes with cursed power, a whisper of death to the forsaken.",
      "Once a soldier’s lifeline, now a harbinger of ruin. Its rounds burn hotter than the fires that made them.",
      "This rifle has put down twenty ghouls in a single night. Their shrieks still linger in its chamber.",
      "Said to have been wielded by the last guardian of a lost city. It did not save them.",
      "Each bullet drinks the light, leaving only empty husks behind.",
      "Its steel is old, its soul is weary, yet it still sings the dirge of battle.",
      "Where this rifle is fired, the crows soon gather.",
      "A cursed weapon, left at the site of a massacre. It has never run dry since.",
      "Bound by blood, tempered in loss. Those who wield it do not do so for long.",
      "The last sound many have heard. The echoes of its shots call the beasts of the abyss.",
      "It spits fire, leaving only charred remains in its wake.",
      "Forged in darkness, blessed by none. The sun has long abandoned its steel.",
      "Dug countless graves, filled them all.",
      "It speaks only in the language of death, and all who listen fall silent.",
      "Its first owner never returned from battle. Neither did the next.",
      "Each bullet is a prayer; none are ever answered.",
      "Neither righteous nor merciful, it simply delivers what is due.",
      "The more it is fired, the more it demands.",
      "Once lost in a forgotten war, it found its way back. It should have stayed buried.",
      "It does not wound, it does not break—it only ends."
    ]
  },
